ed="T" n="0860b07"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0860b07"/><head><date from-iso="+0960-02-09" key="j20717322132856" to-iso="+1127-06-18"><anchor xml:id="begd1e41447"/>宋<anchor xml:id="endd1e41447"/></date><placeName key="PL000000011485"><placeName>杭州</placeName><placeName>真身寶塔寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A013525">紹巖</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0860b08"/><persName key="A013525">釋紹巖</persName>，俗姓<name>劉</name>，<placeName key="PL000000042192">雍州</placeName>人也。母<persName key="A019465">張<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>始娠，夢寤<lb
ed="T" n="0860b09"/>甚奇。及生也，神姿瓌偉；至長也，器度宏深。<lb
ed="T" n="0860b10"/><date key="j20516472052001" from-iso="+0905-02-12" to-iso="+0906-02-01">七</date>歲苦求出家於<persName key="A013526">高安<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，<date key="j20556632056017" from-iso="+0916-02-11" to-iso="+0917-01-30">十八</date>進具於<persName key="A013527">懷<lb
ed="T" n="0860b11"/>暉<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>，凡百經書，覽同溫習。自是遊諸方<lb
ed="T" n="0860b12"/>聖跡，洎入<placeName key="PL000000009925">吳</placeName><placeName key="PL000000013265">會</placeName>，棲息<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000012277">四明山</placeName>，與<persName key="A008355">德韶<lb
ed="T" n="0860b13"/><roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>共決疑滯於<placeName key="PL000000019852">臨川</placeName><persName key="A000174">益<roleName>公</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n2951"/>。遂於<placeName key="PL000000011673"><placeName>錢塘湖</placeName><placeName>水<lb
ed="T" n="0860b14"/>心寺</placeName></placeName>挂錫<ptr target="#n2954"/>，恒諷持《法華經》無晝夜，俄感陸<lb
ed="T" n="0860b15"/>地庭間生蓮華<ptr target="#n2955"/>，舉城人瞻矚。<persName key="A013525">巖</persName>亟命搴而<lb
ed="T" n="0860b16"/>蹂之。以<date key="j20720832072466" notAfter-iso="+0962-02-12" notBefore-iso="+0961-01-25"><name>建隆</name>二年辛酉</date>，經願云滿，誓同<persName key="A003397">藥<lb
ed="T" n="0860b17"/>王</persName>焚身以供養。時<placeName key="PL000000008355">漢南國</placeName>王<persName key="A006774">錢<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>篤重歸<lb
ed="T" n="0860b18"/>心，苦留乃止。尋潛遁，投身<placeName key="PL000000008369">曹娥江</placeName>，用飼魚<lb
ed="T" n="0860b19"/>腹。會有漁者拯之，云「有神人扶足，求溺<lb
ed="T" n="0860b20"/>弗可，衣敷水面，而驚濤迅激，<persName key="A013525">巖</persName>如坐寶臺。」<lb
ed="T" n="0860b21"/>然水火二緣俱為未濟，恒怏惋其懷。乃於<lb
ed="T" n="0860b22"/><placeName key="PL000000055585"><placeName>越</placeName><placeName>法華山</placeName></placeName>安置。續召於<placeName key="PL000000011485"><placeName>杭</placeName><placeName>塔寺</placeName></placeName>，造<placeName key="PL000000011486">上方淨<lb
ed="T" n="0860b23"/>院</placeName>以居之<ptr target="#n2952"/>。<date key="j20759212075950" notAfter-iso="+0971-08-28" notBefore-iso="+0971-07-30"><name>開寶</name>四年七月</date>有疾，不求藥石，<lb
ed="T" n="0860b24"/>作偈累篇示門徒，曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A013525">吾</ref>誦經二萬部，決以<lb
ed="T" n="0860b25"/>安養為期。」<ptr target="#n2953"/><anchor xml:id="beg0860sgsz5"/>跏<anchor xml:id="end0860sgsz5"/>趺坐亡，享齡七十三，法臘五<lb
ed="T" n="0860b26"/>十五。喪事官供，茶毘于<placeName key="PL000000011541">龍井山</placeName>，獲舍利無<lb
ed="T" n="0860b27"/>算。遺骨若玉瑩然。遂收合作石函，寘于影<lb
ed="T" n="0860b28"/>堂。<placeName key="PL000000021536"><anchor xml:id="beg0860002"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>大</sic><corr>泰</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0860002"/>寧軍</placeName>節度使贈太師<persName key="A013528">孫承祐</persName>為碑紀<lb
ed="T" n="0860b29"/>述焉。</p>
